data.description: This stunning single-family residence, built in 2010, is the perfect haven for a growing family, offering 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a spacious 1,568 sq ft of living space. As you step inside, the well-designed layout seamlessly combines functionality with entertaining, maximizing every square foot for both style and practicality. The thoughtfully crafted interior creates a welcoming space that adapts effortlessly to your lifestyle. Venture into the generous backyard with its 8,286 sq ft lot, inviting endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment, whether it's hosting gatherings or envisioning your own private pool oasis. Don't miss the chance to call this property home! Schedule a viewing today!
